0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"OHSAS 18001:"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:32+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"What is OHSAS 18001? Easy ways to implement OHSAS 18001 in UAE\""}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"OHSAS 18001:"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"OHSAS 18001 is an International Standard for Occupational Health and Safety Management Systems. This establishes conditions for an organization, by planning, documenting and implementing a verifiable method for reducing the dangers in the workplace, to control its occupational health and safety dangers and improves its performance.OHSAS 18001 certificationoffers many advantages to both the employer and the worker. Checkout the benefits of OHSAS 18001 so that the organization can improve health and safety."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Reason to implement OHSAS 18001 in your organization"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"OHSAS 18001 standard is implemented in the organization that has great effects. Wizms, best ISO consultant in UAE helps the companies to get OHSAS 18001 certification."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Improves the reputation and credibility - Best ISO consultants in UAE assures the customers that have a commitment to demonstrable management of occupational health and safety, also can enhance the organizations brand image and increase their share value by improving the community relations."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Improve to reduce cost -All the companies in UAE are looking to reduce the cost. The OHSAS 18001 certification can help with this by increasing rating at insurance companies, while reducing occupational health and safety incidents that may lead to lawsuits and deterioration of the organizations image."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Using evidence-based decision making - Make sure that your organization is using accurate data to make your decisions on what to improve, you can greatly increase the chances that your improvements will be successful at the first time, rather than having several unsuccessful attempts. By using this valuable data, it is easy to track your progress, so that you can correct these improvements before you go for the trial and error which can save costs and time."}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Continuous improvement - By holding OHSAS 18001 certification in UAE, the company has to review the improvement continuously, so that the employers can work toward better processes and reduced occupational health and safety hazards in a systematic way in order to improve your brand name and potentially reduce your costs. When a culture of improvement is created after implementing OHSAS 18001 certification, people are always looking for ways to make their processes better that helps to maintain the OHSAS 18001 standard easier."}],"$L2","$L3","$L4"]}],"$L5"]}]}],["$L6"],"$L7"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
2:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Engage the employers - A company must shows their care and concern for occupational health and safety to their employers. By engaging your employees in a group effort to reduce your occupational health and safety hazards, an organization can increase employee focus and retention."}]
